Author: birkomester
Title: [ICO] [Totum]
Body: Attention please!  1. SLN hasn’t been in contact for 3 weeks (October – November) at all and hasn’t answered our managers, so we were looking for a new bounty manager. 2. We informed SLN that we change our token sale dates. 3. It isn’t scam project. We didn’t raise money and didn’t cheat. We just change our token sale dates and should do a lot of updates before it. 4. If someone wants to get evidence (some screenshots that SLN hasn’t been in contact for a long time or that we informed him) or receive additional information, please contact us via support@totum.in 5. Dear SLN, if you have any questions, contact us via support@totum.in too.
